text: Matrayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Matrayevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 940 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 58 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Matrayevo
